e/health-coronavirus-energy-idINKCN22A2MY|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="reuters2">{{cite web|title=Green hydrogen's time has come, say advocates eying post-pandemic world|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronarivus-hydrogen-analysis-idUSKBN22K0MJ|accessdate=2020-06-01|date=2020-05-08|language=en|website=Reuters|archive-date=2020-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200709225611/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronarivus-hydrogen-analysis-idUSKBN22K0MJ|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="reuters3">{{cite web|title=Why The Coronavirus Pandemic Is Creating A Surge In Renewable Energy|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/heatherfarmbrough/2020/05/05/why-the-coronavirus-pandemic-is-creating-a-surge-in-renewable-energy/|accessdate=2020-06-01|language=en|last1=Farmbrough|first1=Heather|website=Forbes|archive-date=2020-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200612192755/https://www.forbes.com/sites/heatherfarmbrough/2020/05/05/why-the-coronavirus-pandemic-is-creating-a-surge-in-renewable-energy/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

