pert|url=https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2020/jun/18/world-has-six-months-to-avert-climate-crisis-says-energy-expert|accessdate=2020-06-21|work=The Guardian|date=2020-06-18|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109112703/https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2020/jun/18/world-has-six-months-to-avert-climate-crisis-says-energy-expert|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Publikation - Der Doppelte Booster|url=https://www.agora-energiewende.de/veroeffentlichungen/der-doppelte-booster/|accessdate=2020-06-21|language=de|website=www.agora-energiewende.de|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105141855/https://www.agora-energiewende.de/veroeffentlichungen/der-doppelte-booster/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=A Green Stimulus Plan for a Post-Coronavirus Economy|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-03-24/green-stimulus-plan-for-a-post-covid-19-economy|accessdate=2020-06-25|work=www.bloomberg.com|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114102754/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-03-24/green-stimulus-plan-for-a-post-covid-19-economy|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Priorities for a green recovery following coronavirus|url=https://www.cbi.org.uk/articles/green-recovery-priorities-following-coronavirus/|accessdate=2020-06-25|website=CBI|archive-date=2020-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929223635/https://www.cbi.org.uk/articles/green-recovery-priorities-following-coronavirus/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 都参与其中。<ref>{{Citation|last1=Weitzel|first1=Elic|title=Are Pandemics Good for the Environment?|date=2020|url=https://www.sapiens.org/archaeology/covid-19-environment/|journal=Sapiens|access-date=2020-07-07|archive-date=2020-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230211535/https://www.sapiens.org/archaeology/covid-19-environment/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 同时，[[联合国秘书长|联合国秘书长]]安东尼奥·古特雷斯提出了六种与可持续性相关的宏观准则来帮助经济复苏。<ref>{{cite web|title=Climate Change and COVID-19: UN urges nations to 'recover better'|url=https://www.un.org/en/un-coronavirus-communications-team/un-urges-countries-%E2%80%98build-back-better%E2%80%99|accessdate=2020-06-25|archive-date=2020-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713045347/https://www.un.org/en/un-coronavirus-communications-team/un-urges-countries-%E2%80%98build-back-better%E2%80%99|dead-url=no}}</ref>

